a big leap into a new type of people,

00:01:26.126 --> 00:01:34.402
who will bring Sahaja Yoga to a much wider
level and that is going to help all of us.

00:01:34.421 --> 00:01:42.441
At the same time I have to tell you, that we all Sahaja Yogis have to understand certain things, which are very important.

00:01:42.464 --> 00:01:47.385
Of course, I was very much pleased with the
