00:01:47.405 --> 00:01:48.295
It’s very good.

00:01:48.311 --> 00:01:52.165
But certain things must be understood very clearly.

00:01:52.205 --> 00:01:54.705
And one of them was that some people,

00:01:54.705 --> 00:01:56.645
of course, come to complain to Me also.

00:01:56.645 --> 00:02:01.095
You must know that, that they said that
the charges were rather too much for them,

00:02:01.118 --> 00:02:06.940
for this programme and that the food was not sufficient

00:02:06.958 --> 00:02:10.470
and some of them didn’t get sufficient food.

00:02:10.498 --> 00:02:12.120
All right, whatever it is.

00:02:12.150 --> 00:02:19.861
so from next time we have to remember that we must keep charges little lower, try to give sufficient food.

00:02:19.861 --> 00:02:22.361
Then I discovered that I was rather angry

00:02:22.361 --> 00:02:27.301
with Christine and I told her that, “How
is it that the food was not sufficient?”

00:02:27.290 --> 00:02:31.880
Then she said it was a caterer. But you
don’t have caterers; that's not proper.

00:02:31.891 --> 00:02:34.690
We shouldn’t have in Sahaja
Yoga any caterers or anything.

00:02:34.710 --> 00:02:37.040
There are Sahaja Yogis; they should cook.

00:02:37.050 --> 00:02:39.260
That’s the best way. There are so many of us

00:02:39.260 --> 00:02:43.314
and we should not arrange with the
caterers because the caterers are,

00:02:43.314 --> 00:02:49.744
you know, they make their own profits and they are not bothered whether everybody has got food or not.

00:02:49.743 --> 00:02:53.114
So that should not happen. Next
time we should have a more...

00:02:53.137 --> 00:02:55.527
I mean, actually I could have cooked for you.

00:02:55.557 --> 00:03:02.927
I’m very good at cooking Myself, but I didn’t know there was a caterer or anything.

00:03:02.928 --> 00:03:09.107
So, this is what one has to see to it, that you should arrange things in such a way.

00:03:09.130 --> 00:03:17.460
And then another thing I have decided tomorrow to open an account in My name, in one of the banks here.

00:03:17.487 --> 00:03:22.450
And so that those who have to send
money for next year’s programme

00:03:22.472 --> 00:03:25.851
should send it there directly, or
they can send it to Christine,

00:03:25.870 --> 00:03:31.359
and Christine has to send all that and keep
a receipt of that and she has to tell Me.

00:03:31.379 --> 00:03:33.531
This is very important; one must understand.

00:03:33.531 --> 00:03:38.666
Secondly, I would say that you all should
have all the accounts properly written down.

00:03:38.666 --> 00:03:41.801
That is one of the most
important things in Sahaja Yoga.

00:03:41.814 --> 00:03:44.521
When I asked Christine, “What
about the accounts and all that?”

00:03:44.521 --> 00:03:47.971
She said that there isn’t any
system like that existing.

00:03:47.991 --> 00:03:50.331
I said, “That’s something surprising.”

00:03:50.331 --> 00:03:57.021
Because in London, though whatever it is, you know
that very well, every penny is accounted for.

00:03:57.049 --> 00:04:03.614
Even I am so meticulous about it, that if I
borrow even twenty p from you or anything,

00:04:03.614 --> 00:04:06.114
I return it, see to it, because it haunts Me.

00:04:06.114 --> 00:04:09.919
And in the same way I think the
accounting is very important.

00:04:09.923 --> 00:04:14.930
One of the reasons why you suffer from money,
may be, that the accounts are not there.

00:04:14.956 --> 00:04:23.350
Must keep accounts, because I may not see the accounts,
but I may just have a glance at it and look at it.

00:04:23.385 --> 00:04:29.070
Actually, I would like to know what sort of
money is coming and what sort of money is going.

00:04:29.070 --> 00:04:32.445
It’s important. Is the Lakshmi
tattwa, which you must look after.

00:04:32.445 --> 00:04:36.725
It’s very important. It’s extremely
important. So next time when I come,

00:04:36.748 --> 00:04:39.964
anything you do, you must have proper accounts.

00:04:39.988 --> 00:04:42.488
And just to show Me. That’s all.

00:04:42.488 --> 00:04:46.848
I am not going to deal with it, but I must
just see. My glances must be on that,

00:04:46.875 --> 00:04:50.878
so that if there is any problem
of the money it can be solved.

00:04:52.313 --> 00:04:56.175
Like, we did, in North America
was a big mess, I must say.

00:04:56.200 --> 00:05:02.175
Last time. It was a very, very big mess,
and the whole thing took so much of money

00:05:02.216 --> 00:05:07.506
and the way it was wasted, er, we must,
because there was no accounting system.

00:05:07.506 --> 00:05:14.456
If Patrick was to be put to the account system that, “We have to give account to Mother of every pie and everything that is important.”

00:05:14.456 --> 00:05:16.762
There he could not have run
away with all that money.

00:05:16.762 --> 00:05:21.436
And despite that, he was a banker, because he didn’t
know where he was spending, what he was doing.

00:05:21.468 --> 00:05:27.166
And if you don’t keep that kind of an accounting, saying that, “This is Mother’s accounts,” you see, what will happen?

00:05:27.166 --> 00:05:30.256
Money will slip out. You’ll over-spend money.

00:05:30.269 --> 00:05:32.356
That’s what exactly happened last time.

00:05:32.356 --> 00:05:35.396
And this time I don’t want it to be repeated.

00:05:35.436 --> 00:05:37.936
This is God’s money; this is His work.

00:05:37.936 --> 00:05:42.306
And we have to be very careful
with every paisa that we have.

00:05:42.321 --> 00:05:44.821
This is a very important thing
which people don’t understand,

00:05:44.821 --> 00:05:49.496
and I was amazed when Christine told Me she has
no accounts of things and amazed how is it.

00:05:49.505 --> 00:05:53.044
She is the leader of New York
and she should have kept it.

00:05:53.032 --> 00:05:56.624
And I’m really sorry that she
had no accounts of anything.

00:05:56.626 --> 00:05:58.784
It really surprised Me.

00:05:58.788 --> 00:06:05.413
How could she do like that? And she knows; she has
lived in London and she knows what is to be done.

00:06:05.428 --> 00:06:09.033
This is another thing, because I must tell you
all these things, because you should not repeat.

00:06:09.036 --> 00:06:12.113
Then another very important
thing I must tell you:

00:06:12.132 --> 00:06:15.902
I felt yesterday while the Puja was on,

00:06:15.902 --> 00:06:22.302
I tried to raise your Kundalini. A terrible catch
of a very worst type on the Heart, Vishuddhi,

00:06:22.324 --> 00:06:27.177
went into the chakra here.

00:06:28.457 --> 00:06:34.147
Now, that means there were some people
who were not fully Sahaja Yogis.

00:06:34.147 --> 00:06:36.989
So, it should never be done.

00:06:37.007 --> 00:06:39.507
Even in France, they did the same thing.

00:06:39.507 --> 00:06:45.469
And I told them, “You shouldn’t get half-hearted
people, just who have come for the Puja.

00:06:45.497 --> 00:06:50.450
If they are friends of somebody or something,
Puja, you have to be very, very cautious.

00:06:50.451 --> 00:06:54.760
Because it gives Me pain.” You don’t want to give
Me pain and don’t want to trouble Me, isn’t it?

00:06:54.793 --> 00:06:58.700
I’ve come here to solve
problems, not to get into these.

00:06:58.727 --> 00:07:02.103
And it was really so painful
yesterday, you have no idea.

00:07:02.125 --> 00:07:04.343
But somehow I managed to take it out.

00:07:04.343 --> 00:07:10.013
So I would tell you, those people
who are not fully realised

00:07:10.013 --> 00:07:12.478
who are not in doubtless awareness,

00:07:12.493 --> 00:07:15.266
you must not have them for Puja.

00:07:15.266 --> 00:07:17.766
It gives Me trouble or they may go off.

00:07:17.766 --> 00:07:22.123
There was one fellow, I told him not to
come in, in France, and he became crazy.

00:07:22.123 --> 00:07:25.493
And then he will go to the jail, he
will go to the people and say

00:07:25.486 --> 00:07:27.986
that, “Because of Kundalini Jagruti I got it.”

00:07:27.986 --> 00:07:31.603
But to see to awaken
Kundalini is not an easy thing.

00:07:31.603 --> 00:07:35.433
And when everybody’s Kundalini is
rising, his Kundalini also may rise

00:07:35.453 --> 00:07:40.038
and may have such a problem that we
cannot solve it. So you be careful.

00:07:40.038 --> 00:07:43.033
First of all, you should be really
very, very strict with people

00:07:43.047 --> 00:07:45.173
that you should say, “You must all become.

00:07:45.173 --> 00:07:47.673
Unless and until you have
become, you cannot come to Puja.”

00:07:47.673 --> 00:07:50.173
And I tell you, this works much better.

00:07:50.173 --> 00:07:53.723
Then everybody tries to be that;

00:07:53.730 --> 00:07:57.043
everybody tries to race themselves.

00:07:57.043 --> 00:07:59.693
That, it’s a competition, sort of
thing, you know, they set into,

00:07:59.693 --> 00:08:02.523
and they say, “We must do this.
Otherwise, how can it be?”

00:08:02.523 --> 00:08:04.223
So they try to improve.

00:08:04.223 --> 00:08:08.423
But if you allow right, lovey-dovey
style, it goes on like that.

00:08:08.423 --> 00:08:14.153
It’s not that. And France, it’s one of them, which
has suffered so much because of this kind of thing.

00:08:14.173 --> 00:08:18.103
And I find in France then the wave
comes up and suddenly it drops down,

00:08:18.103 --> 00:08:22.343
again comes up, goes down, because
there are no solid people there.

00:08:22.363 --> 00:08:26.523
So you have to create really very,
very, very, very solid people.

00:08:26.523 --> 00:08:29.263
That is important, and Puja
is only meant for them.

00:08:29.298 --> 00:08:32.699
Yeah, there may be only five, there
could be only ten; doesn’t matter.

00:08:32.699 --> 00:08:35.876
Not important to have many people for Puja.

00:08:35.909 --> 00:08:38.146
We can have it for programmes. So remember:

00:08:38.179 --> 00:08:41.356
I’m telling you very clearly
anywhere. You want to have a Puja,

00:08:41.356 --> 00:08:46.586
supposing now, say, in, er, San Francisco
or San Diego, you want to have a Puja,

00:08:46.586 --> 00:08:54.006
anything of even of the photograph, then please do not
admit people to come in, who are not realised fully.

00:08:54.006 --> 00:08:57.736
Remember that. Never get them. You’ll have trouble, your children will have trouble,

00:08:57.766 --> 00:09:01.178
your husbands will have trouble
and their bhoots will get into you.

00:09:02.678 --> 00:09:08.198
Because they’ll be so frightened as to face it,
that there could be very serious things happen.

00:09:08.198 --> 00:09:14.664
So remember my words: do not allow people who are
half-hearted, half-baked to come to Sahaja Yoga

00:09:14.664 --> 00:09:19.118
in a way that is in the inner circle.

00:09:20.293 --> 00:09:25.268
Sahaja Yoga has three circles, as you know. One
is the periphery, where people come, go, like that.

00:09:25.295 --> 00:09:28.678
Second circle is where people
come and settling down.

00:09:28.678 --> 00:09:30.498
And third one where they are settled down.

00:09:30.533 --> 00:09:35.463
Only the third one can do the Puja. They only
have the privilege; it’s a special privilege.

00:09:35.463 --> 00:09:37.963
Everybody cannot have that privilege. All right?

00:09:37.963 --> 00:09:41.893
This is one thing, then. Another
thing which really frightened Me was

00:09:41.893 --> 00:09:45.834
the little child here. He
was very badly caught up.

00:09:45.863 --> 00:09:53.354
And now I don’t know why, but I must say
that you must have your vibrations corrected.

00:09:53.354 --> 00:09:55.854
May be something wrong that how
could you not feel the child.

00:09:55.854 --> 00:09:59.854
Means he would have gone mad the way
he was. You don’t know how he was.

00:09:59.869 --> 00:10:02.369
It was very dangerous. It could be with any other child.

00:10:02.369 --> 00:10:07.324
Why I am telling it openly? That it could
be with any other child that can happen.

00:10:07.346 --> 00:10:10.676
So be careful about your children. Be very careful.

00:10:10.704 --> 00:10:14.966
Always feel their vibrations. They,
you see, you are just trustees.

00:10:14.976 --> 00:10:16.826
They are My children.

00:10:16.826 --> 00:10:22.811
I was so amazed, I tell you. And he is so aware,
so intelligent and such a great soul like him.

00:10:22.855 --> 00:10:26.011
And he was suffering within himself, you see.

00:10:26.011 --> 00:10:29.501
Not only him; anyone of them could be
like that, anyone of the children.

00:10:29.501 --> 00:10:31.081
He’s just an example.

00:10:31.081 --> 00:10:36.131
It came to My mind yesterday,
and I was really very much upset,

00:10:36.135 --> 00:10:40.481
very upset, because they
are My children, not yours.

00:10:41.557 --> 00:10:46.177
They are in your trust, and nothing
should happen to My children.

00:10:46.190 --> 00:10:48.477
Otherwise, I’ll take them away.

00:10:48.477 --> 00:10:51.667
You have to look after them.
Keep your vibrations all right.

00:10:51.667 --> 00:10:57.127
Remember that. Never get them. You’ll have
trouble, your children will have trouble,

00:10:57.137 --> 00:11:01.487
See how they are. Look after them. It’s
not the responsibility of one person.

00:11:01.487 --> 00:11:03.987
It’s the responsibility of the whole centre.

00:11:03.987 --> 00:11:07.502
Like, Olympia got lost very much.

00:11:08.488 --> 00:11:10.988
And I was amazed how she got lost so much.

00:11:10.988 --> 00:11:15.348
I went to find out what was the reason,
how this child got into this thing.

00:11:15.348 --> 00:11:19.448
To Olympia, is such a great soul,
and I gave it to Gavin and Jane.

00:11:19.478 --> 00:11:21.368
And why this child is lost?

00:11:21.380 --> 00:11:24.150
Now Jane is gone out there to learn some Sanskrit.

00:11:24.150 --> 00:11:29.590
There was one lady who tried to be
over sort of possessive of Olympia.

00:11:29.590 --> 00:11:31.904
She ruined her completely.

00:11:31.904 --> 00:11:36.160
So, but one thing about English is
that they all are joined together.

00:11:36.167 --> 00:11:39.070
All the children are there. They
always see them in the programmes.

00:11:39.070 --> 00:11:43.669
They are all the time there. Even if they are running, jumping or doing anything, even sleeping; doesn’t matter.

00:11:43.669 --> 00:11:45.509
But they bring the children to the programme.

00:11:45.552 --> 00:11:48.052
So the children are checked all the time.

00:11:48.052 --> 00:11:51.189
And they immediately informed Me about this.

00:11:51.199 --> 00:11:55.939
And we have now arranged her to go to
some other place, not with the parents,

00:11:55.957 --> 00:11:59.479
but she will be staying with somebody
else. So there is no more problem.

00:11:59.479 --> 00:12:01.979
You see, you must know it’s very important.

00:12:01.979 --> 00:12:06.109
Because of their grace, we are getting so many things.

00:12:06.139 --> 00:12:12.408
They are great souls God has given us. They are great
saints God has given us. We have to respect them

00:12:12.408 --> 00:12:17.208
We have to allow them to grow in Sahaja Yoga.
They should not be denied any opportunity.

00:12:17.208 --> 00:12:21.018
They should be brought to the
programmes, they should be tested by you.

00:12:21.018 --> 00:12:23.518
They should be looked after. They are in your trust.

00:12:23.518 --> 00:12:27.128
So if something happens, say,
in San Francisco to children,

00:12:27.119 --> 00:12:33.128
I will definitely catch hold of someone in
San Francisco, why it has happened to them.

00:12:33.127 --> 00:12:35.163
All of you are responsible.

00:12:35.163 --> 00:12:37.977
It’s not only Judy, who is responsible for her children,

00:12:38.029 --> 00:12:40.597
but all of you are responsible for these children.

00:12:40.617 --> 00:12:43.657
It’s not only that he is responsible for that child,

00:12:43.656 --> 00:12:46.567
but everybody is responsible for that child.

00:12:46.572 --> 00:12:52.435
So children are a collective
responsibility; this we must understand.

00:12:52.451 --> 00:12:57.655
Otherwise, we’ll be in trouble because
if you do not look after the saints,

00:12:57.661 --> 00:13:01.271
God is not going to be happy with us.

00:13:01.291 --> 00:13:09.441
That is very important for all of you to look after the
children in such a way that’s a collective responsibility.

00:13:09.441 --> 00:13:12.361
Every child must be looked after.

00:13:13.931 --> 00:13:18.771
Moreover, in England, after all,
because I’m there, I’m very alert.

00:13:18.802 --> 00:13:26.692
And sometimes I find it happened even
in Switzerland something like that.

00:13:26.692 --> 00:13:29.192
And I was amazed how one child was so caught up.

00:13:29.192 --> 00:13:33.169
And then we found that the father was
trying to play some tricks with him.

00:13:33.169 --> 00:13:36.252
And now he might go to jail, his father.

00:13:37.934 --> 00:13:42.064
But you see, you should be alert. What I am trying
to say is you should be all alert about it.

00:13:42.075 --> 00:13:45.174
This is your responsibility. This
is your collective responsibility,

00:13:45.189 --> 00:13:51.224
and I would say that I will hold all of you responsible
if something goes wrong with My children. So be careful.

00:13:51.224 --> 00:13:54.653
They cannot suffer. They are not to
suffer. They have to enjoy life.

00:13:54.653 --> 00:13:56.074
They have to be happy children

00:13:56.079 --> 00:14:01.784
and you have to see their needs and things and they
are a collective responsibility all of us have got.

00:14:01.793 --> 00:14:04.514
They are not the children of the
parents; you must understand that.

00:14:04.514 --> 00:14:07.468
They are your children, they are My
children, they are everybody’s children,

00:14:07.470 --> 00:14:09.970
They are people’s children, they are important things.

00:14:09.970 --> 00:14:13.188
Till they are grown up let them be
here, then we’ll arrange their schools.

00:14:13.188 --> 00:14:15.688
We’ll look after them. They are very precious things,

00:14:15.688 --> 00:14:18.368
extremely precious, all right?

00:14:18.997 --> 00:14:24.842
And this is what I would like to tell you
that no child should suffer in My absence.

00:14:24.849 --> 00:14:28.032
I was quite disturbed because
he's such a great thing, Scott,

00:14:28.053 --> 00:14:33.820
he’s such a great thing. First day I came
here I know. I was so happy to meet him.

00:14:33.840 --> 00:14:36.340
This is a great personality.

00:14:37.400 --> 00:14:41.862
But they should not suffer, you know. They will get
rid of it, but they’ll have to fight it out too much.

00:14:41.862 --> 00:14:45.621
If you help them, if you are alert, you
should see to whom they are talking,

00:14:45.630 --> 00:14:49.390
what they are doing, where
they are going. Keep a watch.

00:14:49.403 --> 00:14:54.840
Be alert, because everybody is under attack.

00:14:54.840 --> 00:14:59.323
All the children are under attack.
All the satanic forces are there.

00:14:59.330 --> 00:15:04.877
You must take them to programmes. That’s one
thing you must do, because there it cleanses out.

00:15:04.891 --> 00:15:08.947
You should not be afraid of taking them to; even
if they sleep off or anything, doesn’t matter.

00:15:08.947 --> 00:15:12.987
Take them in sleeping conditions;
doesn’t matter. It’s all right.

00:15:12.987 --> 00:15:17.817
But they should be there. It works out.
They should be kept always very alert.

00:15:17.833 --> 00:15:23.237
Then the last thing that I have to tell you,
that all of you must clear out your vibrations.

00:15:23.252 --> 00:15:25.547
You all should become really sensitive.

00:15:25.547 --> 00:15:32.889
You should be able to see how much you have improved
in your sensitivity. That’s very important.

00:15:32.889 --> 00:15:35.159
You cannot play games with yourself.

00:15:35.159 --> 00:15:39.399
You have to be very sincere. You
all should know how far you are,

00:15:39.410 --> 00:15:42.799
how far you are identified with your Spirit.

00:15:42.799 --> 00:15:50.522
Is very important, because you are yourself,
you are great seekers, of a very great value,

00:15:50.534 --> 00:15:53.752
and you should not play about with yourself.

00:15:53.782 --> 00:15:55.892
Pay full attention to your Spirit.

00:15:55.892 --> 00:15:58.582
Pay full attention to your sensitivity.

00:15:58.603 --> 00:16:03.796
How far you are sensitive, how far you can feel
others, how far you can understand others.

00:16:03.826 --> 00:16:13.684
And if there is somebody you find is rather, er, bit
too much caught up, just tell Me on the photograph.

00:16:13.684 --> 00:16:15.586
I’ll look after that person.

00:16:15.586 --> 00:16:18.169
We’ll try to improve him or improve her.

00:16:18.176 --> 00:16:21.259
If she does not, then we’ll get rid of her.

00:16:21.259 --> 00:16:25.926
But don’t get caught up yourself;
don’t get into trouble yourself.

00:16:25.951 --> 00:16:32.058
You are saints. You are great things. You
are not to suffer anymore. That’s over now.

00:16:32.058 --> 00:16:34.991
Let Me suffer for you. You
don’t have to suffer at all.

00:16:35.046 --> 00:16:37.281
So you be careful about yourself.

00:16:37.281 --> 00:16:42.001
Now, know your personality, respect
your Spirit and rise in that.

00:16:42.014 --> 00:16:48.311
And don’t in any way allow yourself to be
exploited, or to be tortured by anything.

00:16:48.311 --> 00:16:50.521
Try to rise.

00:16:50.521 --> 00:16:52.640
In Sahaja Yoga, as you know,

00:16:52.640 --> 00:16:56.631
the time as it passes you become
matured and matured and matured

00:16:56.631 --> 00:17:03.191
and, and that’s why we have everywhere, I have
appointed somebody as the leader of the thing.

00:17:03.191 --> 00:17:07.551
One person has to be the leader. I cannot
contact all of you, I’ve said many a time.

00:17:07.551 --> 00:17:11.361
So now, as we have one leader of every place,

00:17:11.368 --> 00:17:14.701
let us have everything done through one leader,

00:17:14.701 --> 00:17:18.408
because if I have to scold I can only scold
one person. That’s Christine in New York.

00:17:18.441 --> 00:17:25.034
Or I can scold Danny in one place like
that, or I can scold some Alexander.

00:17:25.068 --> 00:17:30.263
Now, say, in France they created a
problem for Me this Jean Francois,

00:17:30.293 --> 00:17:33.813
you see, he’s another mad cap, I should
say. I don’t know what to call him.

00:17:33.813 --> 00:17:38.326
I never said anything to him, because
I don’t know French language

00:17:38.326 --> 00:17:40.566
and I don’t know. How will
I speak anything to him?

00:17:40.581 --> 00:17:44.535
He’s just saying that, “Mother said you are
a great leader. You are this. You are that.”

00:17:44.535 --> 00:17:47.361
He’s behaving just like Patrick. Can you imagine?

00:17:48.951 --> 00:17:51.451
Why will I say to him that, “You are like this”

00:17:51.451 --> 00:17:55.333
and if I say, supposing there must
be somebody to translate, isn’t it?

00:17:55.333 --> 00:17:59.103
But he is self-appointed person
there. I’m getting news about him.

00:17:59.145 --> 00:18:01.645
That’s why we've decided not to go to Toulouse.

00:18:01.645 --> 00:18:05.574
But this kind of a nonsense is
not going to work out at all.

00:18:05.574 --> 00:18:11.358
This kind of, you cannot use Sahaja Yoga
for money. You cannot use it for power

00:18:11.374 --> 00:18:13.194
You can only use it for your ascent.

00:18:13.194 --> 00:18:16.886
Like some people think, “I’ve
become the leader of this.”

00:18:16.914 --> 00:18:19.414
How can you become? And, “Mother told me.”

00:18:19.414 --> 00:18:25.223
Of all the things, I don’t know French,
a word. I know three, four words.

00:18:25.229 --> 00:18:27.729
And he doesn’t know English.

00:18:27.729 --> 00:18:32.018
How will I, how will I tell him
something, which I don’t know,

00:18:32.038 --> 00:18:37.638
and that nobody knows about I am telling him in
privacy or can I talk in privacy French language?

00:18:41.399 --> 00:18:46.617
Who is from there? From
Toulouse? Somebody has come? No.

00:18:48.487 --> 00:18:50.546
No, no, no, nobody from Toulouse.

00:18:51.546 --> 00:18:52.956
You are from Toulouse?

00:18:53.996 --> 00:18:57.869
Now what do you say of him?

00:18:57.897 --> 00:19:05.227
It was beautiful because for us
it was a big programme, I mean…And

00:19:05.227 --> 00:19:05.987
Loudly.

00:19:08.477 --> 00:19:17.771
Well, it’s some strange thing because I was going big distance because I have many things and because to get here tonight.

00:19:17.781 --> 00:19:26.949
Because at last tour I was too remembering for (unclear)

00:19:26.964 --> 00:19:34.229
And we have things from Paris, we have things
from Toulouse and we didn’t know how to manage

00:19:34.235 --> 00:19:40.071
and at last, things are at clear tonight. Thank you.

00:19:40.089 --> 00:19:44.751
But I made it extremely clear,
of course, in English language

00:19:44.751 --> 00:19:53.395
but I, I made it so very clear that
it is Alexander with whom I deal.

00:19:53.391 --> 00:19:55.294
Yes

00:19:55.294 --> 00:19:57.794
What do you say, Marie?

00:19:57.794 --> 00:20:09.040
It was extremely clear, but somehow he managed to work out the contrary as to what You said, and to tell other people.

00:20:09.047 --> 00:20:13.170
I mean, this sort of a thing you should
refer back to Me. Thank God it is referred.

00:20:13.170 --> 00:20:14.820
At least it won’t go too far.

00:20:14.820 --> 00:20:20.640
Like, Patrick appointed himself,
self-appointment, the leader of the North America.

00:20:20.636 --> 00:20:24.258
Just imagine. And I never knew.

00:20:24.269 --> 00:20:27.168
Who told him, I don’t know.

00:20:27.179 --> 00:20:29.679
And how much he troubled Me.

00:20:29.679 --> 00:20:36.584
So anybody says like that, you refer it to
Me. Please refer it to Me, immediately.

00:20:36.611 --> 00:20:43.341
And understand that these useless, egoistical
people are trying to be very funny.

00:20:43.371 --> 00:20:48.241
Let him do what he likes in Toulouse, but you do
exactly what Alexander says, and I’ll see him.

00:20:48.249 --> 00:20:53.001
I’ll talk to him. He was a
headache, in India, was he not?

00:20:55.166 --> 00:20:59.527
He was a big headache there and
suddenly now he becomes a leader.

00:21:00.985 --> 00:21:03.485
I just don’t know. So please
don’t do all these things.

00:21:03.485 --> 00:21:09.840
Try to keep one person in charge. I appoint
somebody by understanding that person.

00:21:09.869 --> 00:21:15.349
Everything I understand, and then I appoint
that person. So don’t challenge Me, please.

00:21:15.369 --> 00:21:18.859
None of you should do that. I
would request you not to do this.

00:21:18.878 --> 00:21:25.129
So for all practical purposes, all North
America should work through Christine.

00:21:25.139 --> 00:21:34.449
Christine has to inform Me. I cannot telephone
to all of you. Otherwise, I’ll become bankrupt.

00:21:34.470 --> 00:21:41.905
If we have every telephone is one leader,
say, then what will happen to Me?

00:21:41.916 --> 00:21:44.846
So just keep to one person, all right?

00:21:44.896 --> 00:21:47.396
Is it all right, Steve? Do you understand that?

00:21:47.396 --> 00:21:52.685
You refer it to Christine, all of you. Refer it to Christine.

00:21:53.525 --> 00:21:56.865
All right? She is the main person here.

00:21:56.895 --> 00:22:02.945
And for others who are in their particular
places, like you are there in Boston,

00:22:02.940 --> 00:22:09.817
or somebody is there in Vancouver, like that,
in every place you have one person in charge.

00:22:09.834 --> 00:22:12.067
But let her be in charge of all that.

00:22:12.067 --> 00:22:16.295
I cannot telephone even to San Francisco, to San Diego.

00:22:16.295 --> 00:22:18.795
So you must accept it,

00:22:18.795 --> 00:22:22.527
because she is the one who came all the
way from there to start Sahaja Yoga.

00:22:22.527 --> 00:22:26.259
It is she who started this Sahaja Yoga, isn’t it?

00:22:26.298 --> 00:22:32.099
Like they told me that one Mr. Arizono
came here and you named the thing at,

00:22:32.118 --> 00:22:34.618
he has (unclear: named) even
today that’s how she came here.

00:22:34.618 --> 00:22:39.369
So I know her. There’s nothing wrong
with her. Her vibrations are good.

00:22:39.369 --> 00:22:42.729
She’s perfectly all right. She’s very sensitive.

00:22:42.729 --> 00:22:45.739
If I find anything wrong with her I will correct her.

00:22:45.739 --> 00:22:50.621
Now this is, say, simple plain English
language which I have learned.

00:22:50.609 --> 00:22:56.694
But you do not read into words now,
anymore. It is simple as that.

00:22:56.731 --> 00:23:02.676
I want to make it very clear, because I shouted at her and she was very nervous and she cried and wept and all that; happened.

00:23:02.685 --> 00:23:06.255
Doesn’t matter. But I’ve shouted at
her, because she is responsible.

00:23:06.287 --> 00:23:16.351
She has to assert herself and she has to see and accounts from Boston or from Vancouver should be brought to My notice.

00:23:16.372 --> 00:23:20.831
They should be sent to India. I would
like to see how you people are managing.

00:23:20.861 --> 00:23:28.611
So the one account will be for the future plans and
one account should be, you should manage ad hoc.

00:23:29.755 --> 00:23:34.714
Like you want to have a, say, you want
to have a programme of your own.

00:23:34.715 --> 00:23:37.034
For that you want to collect
some money; is all right.

00:23:37.034 --> 00:23:39.534
But one should never start collections.

00:23:39.534 --> 00:23:44.324
You know, in India. It’s very common in
the West. In India nobody does that.

00:23:44.324 --> 00:23:47.744
Very common; we had a horrible time in London.

00:23:47.744 --> 00:23:52.304
There was one fellow called
Peter Pierce. He came from TM.

00:23:52.304 --> 00:23:55.444
And when I went away he
started a Building Account.

00:23:55.453 --> 00:24:00.130
I don’t know which building it was. Without
the land, without anything, a Building Account.

00:24:00.131 --> 00:24:05.726
And he had taken one house, that
Chelsham Road, and he started it.

00:24:05.726 --> 00:24:12.179
And they collected five thousand pounds, and
no-one knows what happened to that account.

00:24:12.202 --> 00:24:17.739
He took two thousand pounds from My husband.

00:24:17.754 --> 00:24:22.039
Can you imagine such a thing? And within
three months’ time when I was in India.

00:24:22.039 --> 00:24:25.492
But I don’t know why My
husband trusted him so much.

00:24:27.957 --> 00:24:31.452
Then everybody gave him five
thousand pounds and two thousand;

00:24:31.472 --> 00:24:33.972
seven thousand pounds he had nicely with him,

00:24:33.972 --> 00:24:38.108
but the result was such that he became bankrupt.

00:24:38.112 --> 00:24:42.758
And it was such a bad result that the
government asked him to get out of the country

00:24:42.791 --> 00:24:48.139
and he had to leave the country and now he
is in Africa in a very, very bad state.

00:24:48.154 --> 00:24:54.169
Whatever he did for seven thousand
pounds has ruined him completely.

00:24:54.202 --> 00:24:58.209
Imagine; he’s nowhere now.
I mean, he is gone away.

00:24:58.239 --> 00:25:05.946
His wife and children he lost. Everything he lost. And he’s just all alone there in a very bad shape.

00:25:07.655 --> 00:25:10.155
I’ve told you that it is God’s money,

00:25:10.155 --> 00:25:17.186
and these are saints. You cannot collect out of
saints something and spend it the way you like.

00:25:17.216 --> 00:25:20.456
Ravanna used to do that way, and
you know what happened to Ravanna.

00:25:22.293 --> 00:25:24.666
So one should never, because I do not take money.

00:25:24.666 --> 00:25:29.096
That doesn’t mean that anybody should collect
money like that; seven thousands pounds...

00:25:29.127 --> 00:25:31.627
Danny knows all about it.

00:25:33.477 --> 00:25:35.136
It’s very wrong.

00:25:35.136 --> 00:25:39.415
You understand that this is God’s work.

00:25:39.456 --> 00:25:42.335
And you cannot do anything like that.

00:25:42.386 --> 00:25:45.655
This is very important. Otherwise,
money problem will never be solved.

00:25:45.660 --> 00:25:48.725
It will never be solved. For
the time being you might feel,

00:25:48.725 --> 00:25:51.763
but then everything will be wasted.

00:25:51.801 --> 00:25:54.301
So be careful on that; be very careful.

00:25:54.301 --> 00:25:56.801
You have to be honest people.

00:25:56.801 --> 00:26:01.383
Just now that Doudoudiem was telling Me
that in Sudan they are having a shariat

00:26:01.383 --> 00:26:07.475
that anybody steals even a, say,
a fruit, they cut the hands.

00:26:07.502 --> 00:26:09.585
In Sudan; just imagine!

00:26:09.585 --> 00:26:15.652
Now we don’t want that kind of a thing to happen here,
that people should cut anybody’s hands or anything.

00:26:15.652 --> 00:26:23.226
But it is a serious thing, because this
is God’s money; this is God’s work.

00:26:23.226 --> 00:26:28.499
Has to be done with that
understanding and dedication.

00:26:28.499 --> 00:26:38.202
Every paisa that was collected for even Indian tour
was recorded, put into things, every bit of it.

00:26:40.183 --> 00:26:43.712
Yes, I’ll just have that little one.
All right? And thank you, thank you all.

00:26:43.729 --> 00:26:48.034
But I think I speak for everyone here
that everyone will support Christine.

00:26:48.064 --> 00:26:50.564
And I would think everyone here feels the same,

00:26:50.571 --> 00:26:54.919
that she’s the ideal choice to be
the leader of America, North America.

00:26:54.959 --> 00:26:59.429
Thank you, thank you very
much, thank you, thank you.

00:27:04.869 --> 00:27:09.239
And you don’t judge your leaders. Let
Me judge them. All right? Just let Me.

00:27:09.239 --> 00:27:14.089
Try to, try to understand that our, most
of the instructions are coming from Me.

00:27:14.109 --> 00:27:18.415
Because I shout at her and
she looks at Me like this.

00:27:18.439 --> 00:27:22.905
So I said, “What are you doing?
Why are you not strong?

00:27:22.946 --> 00:27:28.196
(Break in this version of the talk. Recommences as She Mataji is talking about photography.)  Horrible!

00:27:28.214 --> 00:27:34.874
But must be something special about you
people, that you handle this subject like that.

00:27:34.909 --> 00:27:39.744
Like today, you see, in the shop, the lady
said, “Oh, You, You had come with Your husband.”

00:27:39.744 --> 00:27:42.744
And I said, “Which one?”

00:27:44.524 --> 00:27:48.834
And that was Raja, Rajabhai Modi. I said,
“That’s My son. What are you meaning?”

00:27:52.244 --> 00:27:55.654
Imagine, what age I must have looked.

00:27:55.678 --> 00:28:01.024
Just imagine. I was wondering what, what camera
she must have used to create such a nonsense.

00:28:02.516 --> 00:28:05.016
Very nice lady, very nice.

00:28:09.880 --> 00:28:12.380
Camera is Mahamaya.

