You remember, Christine, you sent Me one, you’ve
seen… But that’s not American? That is Mexican.

00:32:31.204 --> 00:32:37.774
Yes. Just American china. American
china and I haven’t mentioned that.

00:32:37.779 --> 00:32:40.279
American china is there?

00:32:41.939 --> 00:32:42.769
In silver?

00:32:42.769 --> 00:32:45.269
Old silver, yes.

